quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  10,26,"Abakoze neza bazagororerwa ibyiza (Ijuru) ndetse bazanagira akarusho (ko kubona uburanga bwa Allah). Kandi uburanga bwabo ntibuzigera butwikirwa n’umwotsi ngo bwirabure cyangwa ngo basuzugurike. Abo ni abantu bo mu ijuru, bazaribamo ubuziraherezo"
  10,27,"Naho abakoze ibibi bazahembwa ikibi gihwanye n’ibyo bakoze, ndetse basuzugurike. Ntibazagira ubakiza (ibihano bya) Allah. Uburanga bwabo buzaba bumeze nk’ubutwikiriwe n’umwijima w’ijoro ry’icuraburindi. Abo ni abantu bo mu muriro, bazawubamo ubuziraherezo"
  10,28,"(Unibuke yewe Muhamadi) umunsi tuzabakusanyiriza hamwe bose, maze tukabwira ababangikanyije Allah tuti “Nimujye ukwanyu, mwe n’ibigirwamana byanyu!” Tuzabatandukanya maze ibigirwamana byabo bivuge biti “Si twe mwajyaga mugaragira.”"
  10,29,"“Bityo Allah arahagije kuba umuhamya hagati yacu namwe, kuko mu by’ukuri tutari tuzi ko mutugaragira.”"
  10,30,"Aho, buri muntu azamenya ibyo yakoraga maze basubizwe kwa Allah, Umurinzi wabo w’ukuri, nuko ibigirwamana bihimbiraga bibahungire kure"
  10,31,Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ni nde ubaha amafunguro aturutse mu kirere (imvura) no mu isi (ibimera)? Ni nde ugenga kumva no kubona? Ni nde ukura ikizima mu cyapfuye akanakura icyapfuye mu kizima? Ni na nde ugenga gahunda z’ibintu byose? Bazavuga bati “Ni Allah.” Vuga uti “Ese ntimutinya (ibihano bya Allah ku bwo kumubangikanya)?”
  10,32,"Uwo ni Allah, Nyagasani wanyu w’ukuri. None se ni iki gikurikira (kureka) ukuri kitari ubuyobe? None se ni gute mwateshuka ku kuri (mukareka kugaragira Allah wenyine)"
  10,33,Uko ni ko ijambo rya Nyagasani wawe ryasohoye kuri ba bandi bigometse ko batazigera bemera (Allah ndetse n’Intumwa ye)
  10,34,Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ese mu bigirwamana byanyu hari icyarema ibiremwa bitari biriho kikazanabigarura (nyuma yo gupfa)? Vuga uti “Allah ni We waremye ibiremwa bitari biriho akazanabigarura (nyuma yo gupfa).” Ese ni gute mwateshuka ku kuri
  10,35,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ese mu bigirwamana byanyu hari icyayobora (abantu) mu nzira y’ukuri?” Vuga uti “Allah ni We uyobora (abantu) mu nzira y’ukuri. Ese ukwiye gukurikirwa ni uyobora mu nzira y’ukuri, cyangwa ni utayobora atabanje kuyoborwa? None se ubwo ibyanyu bimeze bite? Ni gute mubona ibintu?”"
  10,36,Kandi abenshi muri bo nta kindi bakurikira kitari ugukekeranya. Rwose gukekeranya nta cyo byamara imbere y’ukuri. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibyo bakora
  10,37,"Ntibishoboka ko iyi Qur’an yahimbwa n’undi wese, uretse ko yaturutse kwa Allah. Ahubwo ishimangira ibitabo byayibanjirije ikanatanga ibisobanuro birambuye ku bitabo (bya Tawurati, Ivanjili n’ibindi). Nta gushidikanya kuyirangwamo, yaturutse kwa Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  10,38,"Cyangwa se bavuga ko (Muhamadi) yayihimbye. Vuga uti “Ngaho nimuzane isura (imwe imeze) nka yo (Qur’an), muniyambaze abo mushoboye bose batari Allah, niba koko muri abanyakuri.”"
  10,39,Ahubwo bahinyuye (Qur’an banahakana) ibyo batari bafitiye ubumenyi ndetse n’ibisobanuro byabyo bitarabageraho. Uko ni ko abababanjirije bahinyuye. Bityo reba uko iherezo ry’inkozi z’ibibi ryagenze
  10,40,"No muri bo hari abayemera (Qur’an) ndetse n’abatayemera, kandi Nyagasani wawe azi neza abangizi"
  10,41,Nibanaguhinyura (yewe Muhamadi) uzavuge uti “Mfite ibikorwa byanjye namwe mukagira ibyanyu! Ntimuzabazwa ibyo nkora kandi nanjye sinzabazwa ibyo mukora.”
  10,42,No muri bo hari abagutega amatwi (ariko ntibayoboke); ese ni wowe wumvisha abatumva kabone n’ubwo baba badasobanukirwa
  10,43,No muri bo hari abakwitegereza (ariko ntibabone ibyo Allah yaguhaye bijyanye n’urumuri rw’ukwemera). Ese wayobora abigira nk’abatabona kabone n’ubwo baba batabona koko
  10,44,"Mu by’ukuri Allah ntacyo ajya ahuguza abantu, ahubwo abantu ni bo bihemukira ubwabo"
  10,45,"N’umunsi azabakoranyiriza hamwe, (bazamera) nk’aho batigeze babaho (ku isi) uretse isaha imwe yo ku manywa, kandi bazamenyana. Rwose ba bandi bahakanye kuzahura na Allah barahombye, kandi ntibayobotse"
  10,46,"Kandi (yewe Muhamadi) n’iyo twakwereka bimwe mu byo tubasezeranya (ukiri ku isi), cyangwa tukakuzuriza igihe cyawe (ugapfa), (uko byagenda kose) iwacu ni ho bazagarurwa. Hanyuma Allah akaba umuhamya w’ibyo bakoraga"
  10,47,"Na buri muryango (Umat) wahawe Intumwa; ubwo Intumwa yabo izaba ije (gutanga ubuhamya ku munsi w’imperuka), bazacirwa imanza mu butabera kandi ntibazarenganywa"
  10,48,Baranavuga bati “Iryo sezerano (imperuka) rizasohora ryari niba koko muri abanyakuri?”
  10,49,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ku bwanjye, nta bushobozi mfite bwo kugira ikibi nakwikiza cyangwa ngo ngire icyiza nakwimarira uretse icyo Allah yashaka. Buri muryango (Umat) wagenewe igihe ntarengwa (cyo kubaho); iyo igihe cyabo kigeze, ntibarindirizwa na gato cyangwa ngo bihutishwe mbere yacyo.”"
  10,50,Vuga uti “Nimumbwire! Ese ibihano bye (Allah) biramutse bibagezeho nijoro cyangwa ku manywa (mwabihungira he)? None se ni iki inkozi z’ibibi zisaba kubyihutishaho?”
  10,51,Ese biramutse bibagezeho ni bwo mwabyemera? (Icyo gihe muzabwirwa muti) Ese ubu (ni bwo mwemeye) kandi mwarajyaga musaba ko byihutishwa
  10,52,Hanyuma ba bandi bihemukiye babwirwe bati “Ngaho nimwumve ububabare bw’ibihano bihoraho. Ese hari ikindi muhaniwe kitari ibyo mwakoraga?”